    <title>DateTimeFormatter类</title>
    <link href="/2022/11/21/DateTimeFormatter%E7%B1%BB/"/>
    <url>/2022/11/21/DateTimeFormatter%E7%B1%BB/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h3><p>DataTimeFormatter类是jdk8在java.time.format包下的类。该类也是一个格式化类。<br>其功能相当于DateFormat和SimpleDataFormat的合体，它不仅可以将日期、时间对象格式转化为字符串，还能将特定格式的字符串解析成日期、时间对象。</p><h3 id="获取DateTimeFormatter对象的3种方式"><a href="#获取DateTimeFormatter对象的3种方式" class="headerlink" title="获取DateTimeFormatter对象的3种方式"></a>获取DateTimeFormatter对象的3种方式</h3><ol><li>使用静态常量创建DateTimeFormatter实例。<br>静态常量有：BASIC_ISO_DATE、ISO_LOCAL_DATE、ISO_LOCAL_TIME等。</li></ol><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pgsql">LocalDateTime <span class="hljs-type">date</span> = LocalDateTime.now();<br>//LocalDateTime类是接口实现类<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">System</span>.<span class="hljs-keyword">out</span>.println(&quot;使用常量创建DateTimeFormatter:&quot;);<br><br>DateTimeFormatter dtf1 = DateTimeFormatter.ISO_DATE_TIME;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">System</span>.<span class="hljs-keyword">out</span>.println(dtf1.format(<span class="hljs-type">date</span>));<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>调用format(TemporalAccessor temporal)方法执行格式化，<br>其中参数temporal是一个TemporalAccessor类型接口，它的实现类有LocalDate、LocalDateTime。</p><ol start="2"><li>使用不同风格的枚举值来创建DateTimeFormatter格式器。在FormatStytle类中定义了FULL、LONG、MEDIUM和SHORT四个枚举值，它们表示日期和时间的不同风格。</li></ol><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pgsql"><span class="hljs-keyword">System</span>.<span class="hljs-keyword">out</span>.println(&quot;使用MEDIUM类型风格的DateTimeFormatter:&quot;);<br><br>DateTimeFormatter dtf2 = DateTimeFormatter.ofLocalizedDateTime(FormatStyle.MEDIUM);<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">System</span>.<span class="hljs-keyword">out</span>.println(dtf2.format(<span class="hljs-type">date</span>));<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>根据格式模式字符串创建DateTimeFormatter格式器。</li></ol><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pgsql"><span class="hljs-keyword">System</span>.<span class="hljs-keyword">out</span>.println(&quot;根据模式字符串来创建DateTimeFormatter:&quot;);<br><br>DateTimeFormatter dtf3 = DateTimeFormatter.ofPattern(&quot;yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss&quot;);<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">System</span>.<span class="hljs-keyword">out</span>.println(<span class="hljs-type">date</span>.format(dtf3));<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="解析字符串"><a href="#解析字符串" class="headerlink" title="解析字符串"></a>解析字符串</h3><p>将指定格式的字符串解析为日期、时间对象。</p><p>使用DateTimeFormatter类提供的parse(CharSequence text, DateTimeFormatter formatter)方法来实现</p><figure class="highlight reasonml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs reasonml">String str1 = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;2019-06-01 07:01:59&quot;</span>;<br>String str2 = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;2019年06月01日 07时01分59秒&quot;</span>;<br><br>DateTimeFormatter dtf4 = <span class="hljs-module-access"><span class="hljs-module"><span class="hljs-identifier">DateTimeFormatter</span>.</span></span><span class="hljs-keyword">of</span><span class="hljs-constructor">Pattern(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss&quot;</span>)</span>;<br>DateTimeFormatter dtf5 = <span class="hljs-module-access"><span class="hljs-module"><span class="hljs-identifier">DateTimeFormatter</span>.</span></span><span class="hljs-keyword">of</span><span class="hljs-constructor">Pattern(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;yyyy年MM月dd日 HH时mm分ss秒&quot;</span>)</span>;<br><br>LocalDateTime localDateTime1 = <span class="hljs-module-access"><span class="hljs-module"><span class="hljs-identifier">LocalDateTime</span>.</span></span>parse(str1, dtf4);<br>LocalDateTime localDateTime2 = <span class="hljs-module-access"><span class="hljs-module"><span class="hljs-identifier">LocalDateTime</span>.</span></span>parse(str2, dtf5);<br><br><span class="hljs-module-access"><span class="hljs-module"><span class="hljs-identifier">System</span>.</span></span>out.println(localDateTime1);<br><span class="hljs-module-access"><span class="hljs-module"><span class="hljs-identifier">System</span>.</span></span>out.println(localDateTime2);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
