    <url>/2022/11/20/%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E8%BF%87%E5%8E%BB%E6%97%B6/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">强调的是过去的某个时间段发生的动作或状态<br><br>结构：<span class="hljs-keyword">done</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="动词变化"><a href="#动词变化" class="headerlink" title="动词变化"></a>动词变化</h3><table><thead><tr><th>情况</th><th>方法</th><th>实例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>一般情况</td><td>+ed</td><td>work—worked; look—looked</td></tr><tr><td>以不发音的e(哑音)结尾</td><td>+d</td><td>live—lived; hope—hoped; like—liked</td></tr><tr><td>以辅音字母加y结尾</td><td>把y变为i+ed</td><td>study—studied; carry—carried</td></tr><tr><td>以重读闭音节结尾且末尾只有一个辅音字母(重读辅元辅)</td><td>双写尾字母+ed</td><td>stop—stopped; plan—planned</td></tr><tr><td>以ic结尾</td><td>+ked</td><td>picnic—picnicked; traffic—trafficked</td></tr><tr><td>特殊情况</td><td>不规则变化</td><td>are-were; is&#x2F;am-was; do-did; eat—ate; go—went; 等等</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="重点句型"><a href="#重点句型" class="headerlink" title="重点句型"></a>重点句型</h3><figure class="highlight applescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs applescript">It <span class="hljs-keyword">is</span> (high) <span class="hljs-built_in">time</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">that</span>) ...<br><br>是时候干做某事了（实际上自己并不想干）<br><br>eg：<br><br>Dont&#x27;t you think <span class="hljs-keyword">it</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">is</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">time</span> you _ smoking.<br><br>A.give up<br><br>B.gave up<br><br>C.would give up<br><br>D.should give up<br><br>答案：B<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="时间状语"><a href="#时间状语" class="headerlink" title="时间状语"></a>时间状语</h3><ol><li>yesterday (morning,afternoon,evening)</li><li>the day before yesterday</li><li>last night </li><li>(week,Sunday,weekend,month,winter,year,century 世纪）</li><li>ago</li><li>this morning&#x2F;afternoon&#x2F;evening</li><li>when引导的状语从句（动词过去时）</li><li>just now</li><li>the other day – a few days ago.</li><li>at the age of 10 （过去年龄段）</li><li>in the old days</li><li>at that time</li><li>in the+整十数年份+s（⋯世纪⋯年代）</li><li>used to do … （过去做…）</li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
